oc1ZRJWhQ">Ly tao - 離騷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BA%A1o/Minh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-gia-hu%E1%BA%A5n/poem-3aa2tlihTrwlAHWnLopSow">Minh Đạo gia huấn - 明道家訓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BA%A1o/author-f6hExEIODG8dBbnhIj50jQ">Trình Hạo</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-t%E1%BB%91ng-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-tam-c%E1%BB%AFu-l%E1%BB%A5c-s%E1%BB%B1-Th%C3%B4i-Vi-chi-nhi%E1%BA%BFp-S%C3%A2m-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-fXfGQ7DzyqV_QDg4qQh5cw">Phụng tống nhị thập tam cữu lục sự Thôi Vi chi nhiếp Sâm Châu - 奉送二十三舅錄事崔偉之攝郴州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Tri%E1%BB%81u/poem-QHtWALJh3ZB-HYEVJm17pA">Triều - 潮</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br></div>	</div>
